{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it a legal requirement for registered sex offenders to notify neighbours",
        "additional_details": "Too many children experience this horrendous abuse and it needs to stop! We need to protect our children from convicted sex offenders and ensure we do everything we can to prevent innocent minors being exposed to traumatic which is life damaging!",
        "background": "We want every single convicted sex offender to be required to notify all neighbours living on their road that they are a registered sex offender. Make it a legal requirement to help protect young children from being put at risk of abuse!",
